column2: SELECT   p.ra,p.dec,p.g,p.r,p.i,  s.z, s.snMedian_r, s.snMedian_g,  s.velDisp,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,  s.chunk, s.boss_target1,  stM.logMass,  p.fiber2Mag_u,p.fiber2MagErr_u,  p.fiber2Mag_g,p.fiber2MagErr_g,  p.fiber2Mag_r,p.fiber2MagErr_r,  p.fiber2Mag_i,p.fiber2MagErr_i,  p.fiber2Mag_z,p.fiber2MagErr_z,  p.extinction_u,p.extinction_g,p.extinction_r,p.extinction_i,p.extinction_z,  p.modelMag_r,p.modelMagErr_r,  p.modelMag_i,p.modelMagErr_i FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS stM ON s.specObjID = stM.specObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.survey = &&&  AND  s.class = &&&  AND  s.snMedian_g > #  AND   s.velDIsp BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.zWARNING = #  AND  (p.g - p.i) > #
